@startuml
title Simplified E-commerce Backend Architecture

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

actor Client

node "Local / Cloud Runtime" {
  component "API Gateway\nNestJS\nPort 3000" as APIGW
  component "Products Service\nNestJS\nPort 3001" as PRODUCTS
  component "Orders Service\nNestJS\nPort 3002" as ORDERS
  database "PostgreSQL\nPort 5432" as DB
}

Client --> APIGW : HTTP REST
APIGW --> PRODUCTS : /api/products
APIGW --> ORDERS : /api/orders
ORDERS --> PRODUCTS : Validate product\nand retrieve price/stock

PRODUCTS --> DB : catalog_products
ORDERS --> DB : orders_orders\norders_order_items

note right of APIGW
Single public entry point
for clients
end note

note right of PRODUCTS
Responsible for
product catalog
end note

note right of ORDERS
Responsible for
order creation and listing
end note

@enduml
